@StandManager_HostAddress = http://localhost:5102

### Listar sabores de pastel
GET {{StandManager_HostAddress}}/api/pastelflavors
Accept: application/json

### Criar um sabor
POST {{StandManager_HostAddress}}/api/pastelflavors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Queijo",
  "description": "Pastel de queijo tradicional",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/queijo.jpg",
  "availableQuantity": 50
}

### Registrar pedido
POST {{StandManager_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Maria Silva",
  "items": [
    {
      "pastelFlavorId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

